'''哈罗德·阿伦德尔·穆迪''' <ref name="Vaughan">David A. Vaughan, [https://books.google.co.uk/books/about/Negro_Victory.html?id=1qs0AQAAIAAJ&redir_esc=y ''Negro Victory: The Life Story of Dr Harold Moody''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books/about/Negro_Victory.html?id=1qs0AQAAIAAJ&redir_esc=y |date=20190414010807 }}, London: Independent Press, 1950.</ref>（Harold Arundel Moody，{{bd|1882年|10月8日|1947年|4月24日}}）是一位在[[伦敦|伦敦]]出生的[[牙买加|牙买加]]医生，1904年穆迪從牙買加前往[[伦敦国王学院|伦敦国王学院]]學習醫學。他曾開展反对种族偏见的运动，并于1931年在[[贵格会|贵格会]]的支持下成立了[[有色人种联盟|有色人种联盟]]。1947年，哈罗德·穆迪在家中因流感去世，享年64岁<ref name="SouthwarkNews">[https://www.southwarknews.co.uk/history/dr-harold-moody-peckham-physician-thought-britains-martin-luther-king/ "Dr Harold Moody, the Peckham physician who ought to be thought of as Britain's Martin Luther King'"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.southwarknews.co.uk/history/dr-harold-moody-peckham-physician-thought-britains-martin-luther-king/ |date=20200610234738 }}, ''{{link-en|Southwark News}}'', 26 October 2017.</ref>。  

